Class AllPathsInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • AllPathsInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<AllPathsInfo>

    public class AllPathsInfo
extends Object
implements Comparable<AllPathsInfo>
    Stores information about a vertex and its paths to other vertices. Paths are not stored individually. Instead aggregate statistics for the paths from a given vertex are stored including the name of the vertex, the number of other vertices the starting vertex connects to, and the total cost of all the paths.
